* Installation

1. Apply org-icons.patch on the latest org-mode code:
    cd path/to/org-mode
    patch < path/to/org-icons/lisp/org-icons.patch
    rm org.elc ; make ; sudo make install

2. Add these lines to your ~/.emacs:
    (setq load-path (cons "/path/to/org-icons/lisp" load-path))
    (require 'org-icons)

3. Restart emacs


* Configuration



